Level Up Congratulations: I prepared a gift.
Guide: Expand the earring slot.
Raise the treasures hidden in the lake on the fishing ground.
Guide: You can use one more ring slot.
Guide: If you join the Blood Pledge, you can get a bleeding buff.
Einhasad's blessing has lost strength, and I'll replenish it this time.
If you join a clan, you can get a bloody buff.
Slayer wears an ax in both hands, alternating at a fast attack speed.
Howl deals damage to all enemies in five spaces.
Crash is probabilistically given additional damage in addition to the default attack.
Tomahawk throws an ax and causes bleeding to the opponent.
Armor Guard can overcome the greater pain the higher your AC is.
Periodic increases your maximum HP.
The higher the level, the higher the level of HP.
Fury is probabilistically triggered by crash.
Titan-Rock will be a chance to counterattack if you are attacked by a short-range attack from the opponent.
Power grip makes enemies far away from you.
Titan-Magic is a magic or technical attack from the opposite, and if damage occurs, it is probabilistically counterattacked and damages the opponent.
Titan-blit is a chance to fight against the opponent if it is a long-range attack from a ranged attack.
Guide: There is also a birthday for a precious character.
Guide: You can change your initial stats by using a candle.
Guide: Do you know Lineage Mobile Hest?
Guide: I enjoy PC room premium service.
Guide: There are many things you need in the Aden shop.
Guide: The fishing ground is in Gluei Village.
Guide: The dragon's dungeon has a dragon and a dragon dungeon.
